      "date": "2012-10-24 20:31:39.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64, CentOS release 5.8/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/8b6fa6dc-1e16-11e2-bd00-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
